OL,3,CTipton households fear their gardens
OL,4,Cwill collapse completely due to
OL,5,Csubsidence
OL,7,FLarge cracks in the ground are tearing
OL,8,Fthrough people's gardens and land in
OL,9,FTipton in Sandwell - with one family
OL,10,Fsaying they fear their outdoor space
OL,11,Fmight fall away entirely into an
OL,12,Fembankment below.
OL,14,FLast August the gardens on a street in
OL,15,FTipton were mostly flat. Now some of
OL,16,Fthem contain massive cracks in their
OL,17,Fgardens and their walls.
