OL,7,FIt's due to subsidence, which
OL,8,Fresidents blame on nearby construction
OL,9,Fworks for the Brierley Hill Metro
OL,10,FExtension
OL,12,FRyan Kumar, his parents Gurpreet and
OL,13,FAsh blame the construction works
OL,14,Fbehind them - where a new tramline is
OL,15,Fbeing built.
OL,17,FRyan told ITV News Central: "It first
OL,18,Fstarted last year there was some heavy
OL,19,Fvibration work that was at the bottom
OL,20,Fof our valley which is part of the
OL,21,FMidland Metro Alliance tramline.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
