OL,7,F"They were doing heavy vibration and
OL,8,Feven the next door neighbours were
OL,9,Fsaying and our house that there were
OL,10,Fcracks in the garden."
OL,12,FRyan's mother Gurpreet suffers from a
OL,13,Frare autoimmune condition that is
OL,14,Ftriggered by stress, her broken garden
OL,15,Fis aggravating it.
OL,17,F"I barely come out into the garden, I
OL,18,Fdon't want to look at it.
