OL,7,F"When this all started, the first
OL,8,Fthing I'd do when I woke up was look
OL,9,Fout the back window and see if the end
OL,10,Fof my garden was still there."
OL,12,FRyan and his parents are not alone.
OL,13,FNext door there are even bigger cracks.
OL,15,FAnother neighbour has also blamed the
OL,16,Fsubsidence for her house sale falling
OL,17,Fthrough. More people are known to be
OL,18,Faffected nearby.
