OL,7,FThe Transport for West Midlands who
OL,8,Fare responsible for the Midland Metro
OL,9,FAlliance said: "We have taken this
OL,10,Fmatter very seriously and fully
OL,11,Funderstand the frustration residents
OL,12,Fare experiencing.
OL,14,F"As soon as we were made aware of the
OL,15,Fissues, we began working with
OL,16,Fresidents and specialist engineers to
OL,17,Fcarry out an investigation to identify
OL,18,Fthe potential cause.
