OL,7,F"Some investigations are ongoing
OL,8,Fbecause the potential causes are
OL,9,Fcomplex given they include unknown
OL,10,Fhistoric ground conditions and
OL,11,Fdevelopments over the years which
OL,12,Fpredate the start of works for the
OL,13,Fmetro.
OL,15,F"We have taken steps to mitigate the
OL,16,Frisks and we have supported residents
OL,17,Fthroughout this process and will
OL,18,Fcontinue to do so as works progress
OL,19,Fwith stabilising the embankment."
